CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1945, pg. 25 reads: "Nuptials - Friends gathered at the home of Mr. and Mrs. Will McQueen last Saturday to celebrate their recent marriage. Shown left to right are Miss Mildred Johnson, Mrs. Carrie L. English, Will McQueen, Randolph English, Mrs. Will McQueen, Mr. and Mrs. Eudell Williams and Miss Elizabeth Johnson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mildred Johnson, Carrie L. English, groom Will McQueen, Randolph English, bride Mrs. McQueen, Mrs. Williams, Eudell Williams, and Elizabeth Johnson, posed behind cake in domestic interior with striped wallpaper
